content: Übersetzung für ' Übersetzung für ' smoked ham ' von Englisch nach Deutsch Neue Wörterbuch-Abfrage: Einfach jetzt tippen! • None Sanjurge is recognized for its Presunto (a smoked ham) and Folar (a type of bread with different kinds of meat). • None Ammerländer Schinken – or Ammerländer Knochenschinken – is a type of dry-cured (and normally smoked) ham produced in the Ammerland area of North Germany. It has PGI status under EU law. • None A bet on the game between the governors of Kansas and Virginia was resolved when Virginia Governor Tim Kaine sent a Virginia smoked ham to the Kansas state capitol. • None The families and their friends have the Mom and daughter prepare meals such as Smoked Ham with boiled eggs and small sandwiches and drinks quite commonly to have palinka on the table and then wait for Fathers and sons to arrive and say a poem (Husvéti Vers) and then spray on their hair with a parfum, Once the Father and son water the Mom and daughters known as "Locsolkodás". • None The officially protected traditional food of Daleszyce and nearby villages is "daleszycka szynka z beczki", a local type of smoked ham (as designated by the Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Development of Poland). • None Black Forest ham (...) is a variety of dry-cured smoked ham produced in the Black Forest region of Germany. • None In Romanian cuisine, the writer's name was given to a "delicatessen" variety of smoked ham. Enthält Übersetzungen von der TU Chemnitz sowie aus Mr Honey's Business Dictionary (nur Englisch/Deutsch).
